    <div class="mid">
      <h2>About</h2>
      <p>osu! UCI is a newly founded osu! club at the University of California, Irvine. We focus around playing and discussing <a href="https://osu.ppy.sh/">osu!</a>, a free, frustrating, but fun rhythm game. Though based in Irvine, any fellow osu! player is free to hangout with us online and offline. If interested, join us in our <a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/osuuci/">Facebook group</a> where we handle most our organization. Keep on the lookout for our weekly events!</p>
      <img class="widthConstrain" src="groupPhoto.jpg"/>
      <p class="caption">Meet the crew!</p>
      <h2>Meetings</h2>
      <p>We play online on Saturdays from 7-10PM PST. Next quarter's in-person meetings are to be decided while we wait for UCI to give us a room.</p>
      <h2>Lobbies</h2>
      <p>During each play session we make multiplayer lobbies in osu! to play in. Given enough players, we try and split into at least two groups to accommodate a wide spectrum of new to experienced players. Find us online:</p>
      <ul>
	<li>Lobby name: osu! UCI (Hard/Easy)</li>
	<li>Password: maxisagod</li>
      </ul>
